[Method]
SetChartType
[MethodDescription]
Sets the chart type. Values: Bar, Column, Pie, Line, Area, Doughnut, Spline, SplineArea
[Parameter]
chartType
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The chartType parameter.

[Method]
GetChartType
[MethodDescription]
Returns the current chart type name

[Method]
SetTitle
[MethodDescription]
Sets the main chart title
[Parameter]
title
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The title parameter.

[Method]
SetXAxisTitle
[MethodDescription]
Sets the X axis title label
[Parameter]
title
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The title parameter.

[Method]
SetYAxisTitle
[MethodDescription]
Sets the Y axis title label
[Parameter]
title
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The title parameter.

[Method]
AddDataPoint
[MethodDescription]
Adds a data point to the default series (Series1)
[Parameter]
label
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The label parameter.
[Parameter]
value
[ParameterType]
REAL
[ParameterDescription]
The value parameter.

[Method]
AddSeries
[MethodDescription]
Adds a new named data series to the chart
[Parameter]
seriesName
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The seriesName parameter.

[Method]
AddDataPointToSeries
[MethodDescription]
Adds a data point to a specific named series
[Parameter]
seriesName
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The seriesName parameter.
[Parameter]
label
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The label parameter.
[Parameter]
value
[ParameterType]
REAL
[ParameterDescription]
The value parameter.

[Method]
ClearData
[MethodDescription]
Clears all data points from all series

[Method]
SetBackgroundColor
[MethodDescription]
Sets the chart background color (hex, e.g. #FFFFFF)
[Parameter]
hexColor
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The hexColor parameter.

[Method]
SetTitleColor
[MethodDescription]
Sets the title text color (hex)
[Parameter]
hexColor
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The hexColor parameter.

[Method]
SetSeriesColor
[MethodDescription]
Sets the color of a specific series (empty seriesName = first series)
[Parameter]
seriesName
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The seriesName parameter.
[Parameter]
hexColor
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The hexColor parameter.

[Method]
SetFontSize
[MethodDescription]
Sets the base font size for chart labels and title
[Parameter]
size
[ParameterType]
LONG
[ParameterDescription]
The size parameter.

[Method]
SaveAsJpeg
[MethodDescription]
Saves the chart as a JPEG image to the specified file path
[Parameter]
filePath
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The filePath parameter.

[Method]
GetLastError
[MethodDescription]
Returns the last error message, or empty string if no error

[Method]
About
[MethodDescription]
Shows control version and information

[Method]
SetShowLabels
[MethodDescription]
Shows or hides data labels inside the chart. For pie: shows category name and percentage when enabled.
[Parameter]
show
[ParameterType]
BYTE
[ParameterDescription]
The show parameter.

[Method]
SetPieExploded
[MethodDescription]
Explodes (separates) all slices in a Pie or Doughnut chart. Has no effect on other chart types.
[Parameter]
exploded
[ParameterType]
BYTE
[ParameterDescription]
The exploded parameter.

[Method]
SetPieExplodeThreshold
[MethodDescription]
Sets the threshold (%) below which slices are exploded. Slices with % of total below this value will be separated. Default: 20. Range: 1-99.
[Parameter]
percent
[ParameterType]
LONG
[ParameterDescription]
The percent parameter.

[Method]
SetDataPointColor
[MethodDescription]
Sets the color of a specific data point by its label. Useful for coloring individual slices in Pie/Doughnut charts.
[Parameter]
label
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The label parameter.
[Parameter]
hexColor
[ParameterType]
STRING
[ParameterDescription]
The hexColor parameter.

